description	"Kyle Katarn

Class: Jedi
Brief Overview:
A saberist/gunner hybrid with Force powers that rewards flanking, skirmishing, and juggling his various options.

^2Weaponry:
- Melee
- Lightsaber
-- Yellow/Red styles
-- Saber/Blaster Defense (1)
-- Blaster Deflect (2)
-- Enhanced Saber Throw (3) ^3[CS1]
- Thermal Grenade (1)
- Trip Mine (1)
- Detonation Pack (1)
- Bryar Pistol (3)
- Stun Baton

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (1) ^3[CS2]
- Pull (1) ^3[CS3]
- Sense (2) ^3[CS4]
- Lightning (1)
- Grip (2)
- Absorb (1)
- Protect (2)

^8Attributes:
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Faller
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

Kyle Katarn was a Force-sensitive Human male Rebel from Sulon who had defected from the Empire, and later a Jedi of the New Order. After learning of Morgan Katarn's death at the hands of Jerec, Kyle chose to continue his murdered father's mission of protecting the Valley of the Jedi. In the process of fighting through Jerec's minions, Kyle managed to teach himself about the Force and the Jedi way."
